# Class: roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionLeftSign (Priority Intersection with Side Road on the Left Sign)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionLeftSign "P-1b: warns drivers on a priority road of a subordinate (non-priority) side road joining from the left at approximately a right angle."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionLeftSign "Priority Intersection (Left) Sign"@en)
SubClassOf(roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionLeftSign roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionSign)

# Class: roadsigns:PriorityIntersectionRightSign (Priority Intersection with Side Road on the Right Sign)

