# Class: roadsigns:RoadSign (Road Sign)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment roadsigns:RoadSign "The central taxonomic hierarchy organized according to the functional and legal roles defined in the Vienna Convention.

A sign placed beside or above roads to give instructions or provide information to road users, conformant with Part I, Annex 1 of the Vienna Convention on Road Signs and Signals (2006)."@en)
