# Class: roadsigns:SymbolFreeSign (Symbol-Free Sign)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment roadsigns:SymbolFreeSign "DL-query helper: any road sign that explicitly carries zero pictograms/symbols (e.g. the plain priority-road diamond, give-way triangle, no-entry bar). Use this in DL queries instead of the open-world-broken \"RoadSign and not (hasSymbol some SymbolRoadSign)\" pattern."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label roadsigns:SymbolFreeSign "Symbol-Free Sign"@en)
EquivalentClasses(roadsigns:SymbolFreeSign ObjectIntersectionOf(roadsigns:RoadSign ObjectMaxCardinality(0 roadsigns:hasSymbol roadsigns:SymbolRoadSign)))

